title: Super Bowl LVI Reaction, NFL Honors, and a long week
itunes:title: Super Bowl LVI Reaction, NFL Honors, and a long week
description:
Rachel Bonnetta and company react to the Rams winning Super Bowl LVI in Los Angeles! First, Rachel recaps a crazy week of Radio Row, NFL Honors, parties, and celebrities, leading up to the Super Bowl. Then, Rachel covers her favorite moments from the game and the epic halftime performance. After that, Rachel shares the best things she saw and heard this past week from the Super Bowl and beyond. Finally, we wrap up the show with early leans for next year's Super Bowl champion and wondering where a couple of NFC quarterbacks might play next season.
